          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "1. Don't skip the keyword review.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " Catalister's AI is good, but I always check the generated title against Google's autocomplete suggestions. A quick tweak can add 15-20% more search visibility.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "2. Use the competitor overlay before committing.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " If a product already has 500+ stores selling it, the margins will erode fast. Look for items with fewer than 50 competitors.",
