          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "3. Test pricing aggressively.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " Catalister's pricing suggestions are a starting point. I've found that going 5-10% lower on high-competition items and 10% higher on unique finds improves both conversion and profit.",
